title: Practical Photoshop - April 2016
description:
English | 40 pages | PDF | 28.1 MB

Practical Photoshops easy-to-follow tutorials show you how to achieve brilliant creative results whether you're repairing an old family picture, having fun combining images or applying artistic effects to a photo. Practical Photoshop offers creative advice and step-by-step tutorials for users of Adobe Photoshop and Elements. Learn the basics, master new techniques to become a better digital artist, or get advanced Photoshop techniques and create stunning designs from your photos. Practical Photoshop is the magazine that makes sensational images simple
